@startuml
title E-Ticket (TicketInstance) Lifecycle - 3.8 (TicketInstanceStatus)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEECFB
  BorderColor #8B7FD6
  FontColor #1A1A1A
  ArrowColor #444444
}
hide empty description

[*] --> VALID : Booking confirmed\n(e-ticket + QR issued)
VALID --> USED : Partner staff checks in at gate\n(POST /api/staff/checkin/:token)
VALID --> EXPIRED : Booking cancelled by partner /\nnot used
VALID --> REFUNDED : Refund processed
USED --> [*]
EXPIRED --> [*]
REFUNDED --> [*]

USED : Cannot be cancelled/refunded
@enduml
